365
00:23:53.351 --> 00:23:54.769
BOSCO:
<i>Finally.</i>

366
00:23:54.769 --> 00:23:58.981
<i>When all the cons eat.
I can think.</i>

367
00:24:00.691 --> 00:24:03.027
(indistinct chatter. laughter)

368
00:24:12.620 --> 00:24:14.872
