384
00:25:20.938 --> 00:25:23.608
(birds screeching quietly)

385
00:25:26.736 --> 00:25:29.030
<i>If freedom's a state of mind.</i>

386
00:25:29.030 --> 00:25:32.200
<i>I guess my dream
should be enough.</i>

387
00:25:32.200 --> 00:25:34.452
