388
00:25:35.244 --> 00:25:37.914
HUNT: <i>Man. they built this
place just for you.</i>

389
00:25:37.914 --> 00:25:41.626
OFFICER (distorted):
<i>Inmate Quawntay Adams.</i>

390
00:25:41.626 --> 00:25:44.337
Where's your father?

391
00:25:46.130 --> 00:25:48.966
BOSCO:
<i>But dreams ain't freedom.</i>

392
00:25:50.259 --> 00:25:51.302
MAN:
<i>Hey!</i>

393
00:25:51.302 --> 00:25:53.012
HUNT:
<i>There's only one way this ends.</i>

394
00:25:53.012 --> 00:25:55.848
BOSCO (echoing): You're gonna
do this shit to me?!

395
00:25:56.641 --> 00:25:58.976
You're exactly like him.

396
00:26:03.231 --> 00:26:06.109
BOSCO:
<i>I ain't content with dreaming.</i>

397
00:26:06.109 --> 00:26:08.194
♪ ♪

398
00:26:13.116 --> 00:26:15.451
<i>There's information everywhere.</i>

399
00:26:15.451 --> 00:26:17.078
(keys jingling)

400
00:26:17.078 --> 00:26:18.788
<i>Judging from the click-clack
